name: GANdinsky 3D - Nothing Natural - Variant 01
description: I stumbled on this beautiful disaster of a 5G tower distressed with colors from various Kandinsky artworks using Playform GAN AI processing. Really speaks to how unnatural and toxic 5G is, yet you can't visibly see the damage it's doing to all living things.
